          "The key identity is that in this basis the components of any $\\mathbf t$ are $\\alpha=\\mathbf t\\cdot\\mathbf a',\\ \\beta=\\mathbf t\\cdot\\mathbf b',\\ \\gamma=\\mathbf t\\cdot\\mathbf c'$, because the dual satisfies $\\mathbf a_i\\cdot\\mathbf a_j'=\\delta_{ij}$.",
